description: Devin West My last day of being in my 20's id like to share 30 things ive found important the last 10years...  1.trust your instincts they are usually on point.  2.Learn a code of ethics and live by it.I live by love,respect and Loyalty.LRL.  3.Keep god close to your heart when you begin to stray you look back and realize how your happy trying to do good to others and yourself.  4.Nothing is worth fighting about with ones you love.NOTHING.let it go.  5.Dont trust a teenager under any circumstances remember how you were?  6.Everything in life is negotiable.EVERYTHING.  7.Never pay too much for something you want.theres always a better deal to be had.patience.  8.Dont fight for anyone to stay in your life.If the feeling is mutual they will give just the same back.  9.Love others more than yourself.Be giving and kind.But not to the point you loose sight of yourself.  10.Dad always knows more than you.Listen and take it in.But create your own ideals.  11.Never trust a fart.Especially after mexicsn food.  12.Concerts are fun but always uber it.ALWAYS.the promise of only a beer always gets replaced with a gallon.  13.Its ok to be a rebel.Within reason.  14.Eat more vegetables.  15.Dont cheat yourself your worth more than you think when you value yourself.  16.If a woman is not up front with what she wants out of you dont waste your time.Invest in dating.take your time.  17.Dont get married in vegas. üòÇ üòÇ  on hope of love.  18.Dont buy a BMW to impress.Keep your fucking truck!  19.Try new things and be open minded.  20.Show respect even when disrespected.Your heart and others will thankyou later.  21.FUCKIT is always an option just make sure you commit to it.Let it go.dont go back.  22.Be single untill you find yourself.Your mate will be happier with a confident self sufficient man.  23.Only buy quality its worth it.You save money in the long run.  24.If you have to protect yourself.Have proper witnesses.Or make sure your justified.Your rapp sheet and record will thankyou.  25.A bird in the hand really is worth 2 in the bush.  26.Wake everyday happy.This could be your last and give thanks to god.  27.Always be truthful even if its ugly.Except to the boys in blue and black.save your own ass with lies.  28.Only buy Glock,colt,remington,Sig sauer, or ruger.Every other gun is crap except HK which is over priced.  29.Adapt to hard situations rather than fold and feel sorry for yourself.Noone wants to hear your drama.They wana see you rise like the phoenix from the flames.  30.Be yourself dont let anyone change who you are inside.  IM SURE there are 200 more good things i can say.But cheers enjoy and live it up.Life is good. üòÑ
